{
  "version": "Notebook/1.0",
  "items": [
    {
      "type": 1,
      "content": {
        "json": "# CAMS-742 Trustee Name Management Metrics\n\nSuccess metrics for CAMS-742: last-name sort adoption and post-launch name correction patterns.\n\n**Measurements:**\n- **Sort adoption** — trustee list page visits proxy for last-name sort usage (sort is always applied since 742; every list load uses it)\n- **Name edits** — `AUDIT_NAME` history entries created since launch, segmented by migrated vs non-migrated trustees to identify data correction patterns from migration"
      },
      "name": "header"
    },
    {
      "type": 9,
      "content": {
        "version": "KqlParameterItem/1.0",
        "parameters": [
          {
            "id": "TimeRange",
            "version": "KqlParameterItem/1.0",
            "name": "TimeRange",
            "type": 4,
            "isRequired": true,
            "value": {
              "durationMs": 2592000000
            },
            "typeSettings": {
              "selectableValues": [
                {
                  "durationMs": 86400000
                },
                {
                  "durationMs": 172800000
                },
                {
                  "durationMs": 604800000
                },
                {
                  "durationMs": 1209600000
                },
                {
                  "durationMs": 2419200000
                },
                {
                  "durationMs": 2592000000
                },
                {
                  "durationMs": 5184000000
                },
                {
                  "durationMs": 7776000000
                }
              ]
            },
            "label": "Time Range",
            "timeContext": {
              "durationMs": 86400000
            }
          }
        ],
        "style": "pills",
        "queryType": 0,
        "resourceType": "microsoft.insights/components"
      },
      "name": "parameters"
    },
    {
      "type": 1,
      "content": {
        "json": "---\n## Sort-by-Last-Name Adoption\nBecause last-name sort is always applied since CAMS-742, every visit to the trustee list page represents a user interacting with the sorted view. High and sustained page visit counts confirm the feature is in active use."
      },
      "name": "sort-adoption-header"
    },
    {
      "type": 3,
      "content": {
        "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
        "query": "pageViews\n| where timestamp {TimeRange}\n| where url contains \"/trustees\"\n| summarize TrusteeListVisits = count()",
        "size": 3,
        "title": "Trustee List Page Visits",
        "timeContextFromParameter": "TimeRange",
        "queryType": 0,
        "resourceType": "microsoft.insights/components",
        "visualization": "tiles",
        "tileSettings": {
          "titleContent": {},
          "leftContent": {
            "columnMatch": "TrusteeListVisits",
            "formatter": 12,
            "formatOptions": {
              "palette": "blue"
            },
            "numberFormat": {
              "unit": 0,
              "options": {
                "style": "decimal",
                "useGrouping": true
              }
            }
          },
          "showBorder": true
        }
      },
      "customWidth": "25",
      "name": "sort-visit-count-kpi"
    },
    {
      "type": 3,
      "content": {
        "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
        "query": "pageViews\n| where timestamp {TimeRange}\n| where url contains \"/trustees\"\n| summarize UniqueUsers = dcount(user_Id)",
        "size": 3,
        "title": "Unique Users Viewing Trustee List",
        "timeContextFromParameter": "TimeRange",
        "queryType": 0,
        "resourceType": "microsoft.insights/components",
        "visualization": "tiles",
        "tileSettings": {
          "titleContent": {},
          "leftContent": {
            "columnMatch": "UniqueUsers",
            "formatter": 12,
            "formatOptions": {
              "palette": "blue"
            },
            "numberFormat": {
              "unit": 0,
              "options": {
                "style": "decimal",
                "useGrouping": true
              }
            }
          },
          "showBorder": true
        }
      },
      "customWidth": "25",
      "name": "sort-unique-users-kpi"
    },
    {
      "type": 3,
      "content": {
        "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
        "query": "customEvents\n| where customDimensions.moduleName == \"SYNC-TRUSTEE-742-METRICS\"\n| where name == \"DataflowHandlerComplete\"\n| where timestamp {TimeRange}\n| extend activeTrustees = toint(customDimensions.trusteeFetchedCount)\n| summarize LatestCount = max(activeTrustees) by Day = startofday(timestamp)\n| order by Day desc\n| take 1\n| project ActiveTrustees = LatestCount",
        "size": 3,
        "title": "Active Trustees (latest)",
        "timeContextFromParameter": "TimeRange",
        "queryType": 0,
        "resourceType": "microsoft.insights/components",
        "visualization": "tiles",
        "tileSettings": {
          "titleContent": {},
          "leftContent": {
            "columnMatch": "ActiveTrustees",
            "formatter": 12,
            "formatOptions": {
              "palette": "blue"
            },
            "numberFormat": {
              "unit": 0,
              "options": {
                "style": "decimal",
                "useGrouping": true
              }
            }
          },
          "showBorder": true
        }
      },
      "customWidth": "25",
      "name": "active-trustees-kpi"
    },
    {
      "type": 3,
      "content": {
        "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
        "query": "pageViews\n| where timestamp {TimeRange}\n| where url contains \"/trustees\"\n| summarize TrusteeListVisits = count() by Day = startofday(timestamp)\n| order by Day asc",
        "size": 0,
        "title": "Trustee List Page Visits Over Time",
        "timeContextFromParameter": "TimeRange",
        "queryType": 0,
        "resourceType": "microsoft.insights/components",
        "visualization": "linechart",
        "chartSettings": {
          "xAxis": "Day",
          "showDataPoints": true,
          "seriesLabelSettings": [
            {
              "seriesName": "TrusteeListVisits",
              "label": "Page Visits",
              "color": "blue"
            }
          ],
          "ySettings": {
            "numberFormatSettings": {
              "unit": 0,
              "options": {
                "style": "decimal",
                "useGrouping": true
              }
            }
          }
        }
      },
      "name": "sort-adoption-trend"
    },
    {
      "type": 1,
      "content": {
        "json": "---\n## Name Edit Correction Patterns\nCounts of trustee name field edits (`AUDIT_NAME`) since launch, measured each day by the `SYNC-TRUSTEE-742-METRICS` dataflow. Segmented by migrated vs non-migrated to surface whether migration introduced data quality issues that users are now correcting."
      },
      "name": "name-edits-header"
    },
    {
      "type": 3,
      "content": {
        "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
        "query": "customEvents\n| where customDimensions.moduleName == \"SYNC-TRUSTEE-742-METRICS\"\n| where name == \"DataflowHandlerComplete\"\n| where timestamp {TimeRange}\n| extend total = toint(customDimensions.nameEditsTotal)\n| summarize TotalNameEdits = sum(total)",
        "size": 3,
        "title": "Total Name Edits Since Launch",
        "timeContextFromParameter": "TimeRange",
        "queryType": 0,
        "resourceType": "microsoft.insights/components",
        "visualization": "tiles",
        "tileSettings": {
          "titleContent": {},
          "leftContent": {
            "columnMatch": "TotalNameEdits",
            "formatter": 12,
            "formatOptions": {
              "palette": "blue"
            },
            "numberFormat": {
              "unit": 0,
              "options": {
                "style": "decimal",
                "useGrouping": true
              }
            }
          },
          "showBorder": true
        }
      },
      "customWidth": "33",
      "name": "name-edits-total-kpi"
    },
    {
      "type": 3,
      "content": {
        "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
        "query": "customEvents\n| where customDimensions.moduleName == \"SYNC-TRUSTEE-742-METRICS\"\n| where name == \"DataflowHandlerComplete\"\n| where timestamp {TimeRange}\n| extend migrated = toint(customDimensions.nameEditsMigrated)\n| summarize MigratedEdits = sum(migrated)",
        "size": 3,
        "title": "Name Edits — Migrated Trustees",
        "timeContextFromParameter": "TimeRange",
        "queryType": 0,
        "resourceType": "microsoft.insights/components",
        "visualization": "tiles",
        "tileSettings": {
          "titleContent": {},
          "leftContent": {
            "columnMatch": "MigratedEdits",
            "formatter": 12,
            "formatOptions": {
              "palette": "orange"
            },
            "numberFormat": {
              "unit": 0,
              "options": {
                "style": "decimal",
                "useGrouping": true
              }
            }
          },
          "showBorder": true
        }
      },
      "customWidth": "33",
      "name": "name-edits-migrated-kpi"
    },
    {
      "type": 3,
      "content": {
        "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
        "query": "customEvents\n| where customDimensions.moduleName == \"SYNC-TRUSTEE-742-METRICS\"\n| where name == \"DataflowHandlerComplete\"\n| where timestamp {TimeRange}\n| extend nonMigrated = toint(customDimensions.nameEditsNonMigrated)\n| summarize NonMigratedEdits = sum(nonMigrated)",
        "size": 3,
        "title": "Name Edits — Non-Migrated Trustees",
        "timeContextFromParameter": "TimeRange",
        "queryType": 0,
        "resourceType": "microsoft.insights/components",
        "visualization": "tiles",
        "tileSettings": {
          "titleContent": {},
          "leftContent": {
            "columnMatch": "NonMigratedEdits",
            "formatter": 12,
            "formatOptions": {
              "palette": "green"
            },
            "numberFormat": {
              "unit": 0,
              "options": {
                "style": "decimal",
                "useGrouping": true
              }
            }
          },
          "showBorder": true
        }
      },
      "customWidth": "33",
      "name": "name-edits-non-migrated-kpi"
    },
    {
      "type": 3,
      "content": {
        "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
        "query": "customEvents\n| where customDimensions.moduleName == \"SYNC-TRUSTEE-742-METRICS\"\n| where name == \"DataflowHandlerComplete\"\n| where timestamp {TimeRange}\n| extend\n    migrated = toint(customDimensions.nameEditsMigrated),\n    nonMigrated = toint(customDimensions.nameEditsNonMigrated)\n| summarize\n    MigratedEdits = sum(migrated),\n    NonMigratedEdits = sum(nonMigrated)\n    by Day = startofday(timestamp)\n| order by Day asc",
        "size": 0,
        "title": "Name Edits Over Time — Migrated vs Non-Migrated",
        "timeContextFromParameter": "TimeRange",
        "queryType": 0,
        "resourceType": "microsoft.insights/components",
        "visualization": "linechart",
        "chartSettings": {
          "xAxis": "Day",
          "showDataPoints": true,
          "seriesLabelSettings": [
            {
              "seriesName": "MigratedEdits",
              "label": "Migrated Trustees",
              "color": "orange"
            },
            {
              "seriesName": "NonMigratedEdits",
              "label": "Non-Migrated Trustees",
              "color": "green"
            }
          ],
          "ySettings": {
            "numberFormatSettings": {
              "unit": 0,
              "options": {
                "style": "decimal",
                "useGrouping": true
              }
            }
          }
        }
      },
      "name": "name-edits-trend"
    }
  ],
